"v.联合，合并 【英】 v. 联合，合并(to unite or merge into a single body; mix) 【考】 反义词：disaggregat e(分散); bifurcate(分叉); fragment(分裂) 【记】 co+al=ally(联盟)+es ce→一起联盟→联合 【例】 The three old parties coalesced to form a new one. v. (政党、断骨、伤口)结合(到一起形成一个整体) 【例】The two parties coalesced into a new one 两个政党合并成了一个. 【记】co共同, al = ally联盟－共同联盟－结合coal(n 煤): 由非结晶碳、有机化合物和无机化合物组成－结合 【反】disaggregate(v 使崩溃; 分解); bifurcate(v 分叉); polarize(v 使两极分化) 【记】coal 煤是由植物，土，石头等结合而成 coalesce (v.)  1540s, from Latin coalescere ""to unite, grow together, become one in growth,"" from com- ""together"" (see co-) + alescere ""to grow up"" (see adolescent). Related: Coalesced; coalescing; coalescence; coalescent."
